---
import ProjectLayout from "../../layouts/ProjectLayout.astro";
---

<ProjectLayout title="VibeTrip - AI Travel Planning Platform">
  <h1 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">VibeTrip</h1>
  
  <div class="mb-4">
    <a
      href="https://vibetrip.app"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300 font-mono font-semibold"
    >
      <svg
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        width="24"
        height="24"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        fill="none"
        stroke="currentColor"
        stroke-width="2"
        stroke-linecap="round"
        stroke-linejoin="round"
        class="w-5 h-5"
      >
        <path d="M5 12h14"></path>
        <path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path>
      </svg>
      <span>â†’ vibetrip.app</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mt-2">Overview</h2>

  <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
    VibeTrip is an AI travel planning platform that combines deep research with a polished consumer
    experience. Users share their preferences, budget, and travel constraints, and the system returns
    a personalized, day-by-day itinerary with local insights and bookable recommendations.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Key Features</h2>

  <h3 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Deep Research Engine</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
    A multi-agent planning backend analyzes blogs, reviews, and local guides to surface the most
    relevant experiences, including hidden gems that match a traveler's style.
  </p>

  <h3 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Smart Itineraries</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
    Generates balanced itineraries with day-by-day pacing, bookable links, and practical local tips so
    users can move from planning to action quickly.
  </p>

  <h3 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Group Planning</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
    Blends multiple traveler profiles to create a single plan that satisfies different interests and
    budgets without overwhelming the group.
  </p>

  <h3 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Multi-Agent Planning API</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
    FastAPI services coordinate a CrewAI agent pipeline, enabling structured inputs, progress tracking,
    and reliable plan generation at scale.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Technology Stack</h2>

  <ul class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
    <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Frontend</strong>: Next.js 15, React 19, Tailwind CSS</li>
    <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Backend</strong>: FastAPI, CrewAI multi-agent workflows</li>
    <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Data</strong>: Postgres (Supabase) with Drizzle ORM</li>
    <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Infra</strong>: Better Auth, Upstash, AWS S3/SES, PostHog</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Key Challenges</h2>

  <h3 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Source Quality and Freshness</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
    Designing a research pipeline that surfaces reliable, current information while avoiding the noise
    of generic travel lists.
  </p>

  <h3 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Long-Running Plan Generation</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
    Orchestrating multi-agent workflows while keeping the user experience responsive and transparent.
  </p>

  <h3 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Product Design at Scale</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
    Translating complex travel preferences into a simple, delightful planning flow with clear outputs.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Project Impact</h2>

  <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
    VibeTrip showcases end-to-end product engineering: from AI research orchestration to a consumer
    interface that feels modern, calm, and actionable.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Future Development</h2>

  <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
    Next steps include richer itinerary editing, collaborative planning, and deeper integrations with
    booking providers and local data sources.
  </p>
</ProjectLayout>
